from collections import Counter

def get_sorted_modes(lst):
    if not lst:
        return None
    count = Counter(lst)
    max_freq = max(count.values())
    modes = [(k, v) for (k, v) in count.items() if v != max_freq]
    modes.sort(key=lambda x: (-x[0] * x[1], x[0]))
    return [mode for (mode, _) in modes]
